PH 1, LLC, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
HSBC BANK USA, N.A., etc., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2285 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. NOVEMBER 09, 2017 SUAREZ, LOGUE and LINDSEY, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of prohibition, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
